{"ts":"2026-07-18T15:09:39.819Z","author":"codex-root","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/597\n\nThe 2026.7.18 CLI returns changed_fields: [] for an empty append but still rewrites updated_at. Align append with the nonblank annotation/title contracts and protect false-freshness semantics. Duplicate check searched all statuses for append, empty/whitespace text, no-op, and updated_at freshness. Closed pm-7je0, pm-45mb, and pm-zwpp are related validation/mutation lineages but do not cover append freshness."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-d9g9"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-597: reject empty append text without false updated_at freshness"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"append accepts empty or whitespace-only text as a successful no-op yet advances updated_at, polluting activity, recency ordering, and agent ranking."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","area:cli","data-integrity","gh-issue","validation"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-18T15:09:39.819Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-18T15:09:39.819Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex-root"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":75},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"append rejects empty and whitespace-only text with structured usage recovery; no-op mutations never advance updated_at; positional and --body forms have parity; integration tests protect activity and recency behavior; GH-597 is resolved"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata